Author: ashaed31
Text: Right?! I don't even feel hungry anymore even though I'm undereating every day. I can't even imagine eating the insane amount of calories I need to maintain weight, cause I feel like I'd be uncomfortably full all the time

Author: wild_banana_cookie
Text: Yup. People always comment on how little I eat but it feels so normal to me now that theres no other way to go about things.
